reviewText: This movie is awesome and it's crazy to find out that many don't know about this. They should make a remake of this ladies, right along side the male 5 Deadly Venoms version.

I had a feeling the movie would be weak but I tried it anyway. Saw the first 15 minutes. Then took it to the Used video store & sold it for Challege of the Lady Ninja ( which also is terrible). Avoid this movie at all cost.
